description: East Broadway Brownstone, 2 beds, 2 bath condo with deeded outside parking. Features include a master suite with private full renovated private bath and in unit laundry, A renovated stainless steel kitchen that flows into the dining area and living room all leading out onto a spacious private deck with some views of the Boston skyline. Nine-foot ceilings, deeded storage, professionally managed condo association and great walking location. There are four condo association owned rental units (apartments) that help defray common area expenses. Available for immediate occupancy.
